title: (Thurs Full Show) Who Is The Employee Of The Month for October? + Behind-The -Scenes Show Drama + Lunchbox Spills The Tea On Eddie
itunes:title: (Thurs Full Show) Who Is The Employee Of The Month for October? + Behind-The -Scenes Show Drama + Lunchbox Spills The Tea On Eddie
description:
The Employee of the Month was chosen, and it was close between two people! Find out who it was and who on the show is now blocked from getting it for the next three months. And hear how it's created some drama with the show behind-the-scenes with the fight Eddie got on camera. Then, Lunchbox spills the tea about something Eddie is doing that is making the internet in the studio slow.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
